00:10:06,786 --> 00:10:09,139
zogt er, "du host farshtanen vos ikh hob dir gezogt?

191
00:10:09,139 --> 00:10:13,637
kh'hob gezogt ikh darf hobn biz morgn in der fri tsvey tsimern far fir ofitsirn."

