193
00:10:16,975 --> 00:10:21,264
hot er aroysgekhapt dem revolver un hot im geshosn dort oyfn plats, antkegn di froy.

194
00:10:21,264 --> 00:10:24,995
deys iz bald gevorn tseshpreyt in di gantse shtot, fun eyn,

