00:10:24,995 --> 00:10:27,970
fun eyn oyer in andern iz geganen, yeder hot alts

196
00:10:27,970 --> 00:10:29,556
gevust fun der mayse.

197
00:10:29,977 --> 00:10:32,777
hot men gezen az di mayse iz zeyer shlekht.

198
00:10:32,978 --> 00:10:35,518
ober s'iz nishto keyn breyre.

199
00:10:35,518 --> 00:10:38,934
deys iz dos. di tsayt iz gegangen nokh azoy

200
00:10:38,934 --> 00:10:41,117
biz tsvey un fertsiker yor.

201
00:10:41,117 --> 00:10:43,539
mit farshidene sanktsyes, mit farshidene

202
00:10:43,539 --> 00:10:48,367
zakhn vos yidn hobn nisht getort. m'hot gekhapt, m'hot a sakh farshpart, m'hot aroysgelozt,

203
00:10:48,367 --> 00:10:50,825
vifl zey hobn gekent hobn zikh nokh o- oysgekoyft,

204
00:10:50,825 --> 00:10:53,386
vayl s'iz geven di langstike vos zenen nokh gevezn, vos

205
00:10:53,386 --> 00:10:54,994
zenen gevezn bay di rumener,

206
00:10:54,994 --> 00:10:58,794
nor zikh ⟨iber⟩getun dos rekl oyf di andere zayt un zey zenen bald gevorn bay di rumener

207
00:10:58,794 --> 00:11:02,514
firers. un se hot nokh alts gedoyert. in tsvey un fertsiker yor

208
00:11:02,514 --> 00:11:05,085
iz geven a mobilizatsye.

209
00:11:05,085 --> 00:11:07,850
di ungarn hobn mobilizirt

210
00:11:07,850 --> 00:11:10,835
ale mener fun der shtot

211
00:11:11,304 --> 00:11:13,568
in MUNKÁSSZÁZAD,

212
00:11:13,568 --> 00:11:15,808
in arbayts-dinst arayn.

213
00:11:15,808 --> 00:11:17,836
un ikh bin geven tsishn deye.

214
00:11:19,111 --> 00:11:24,229
un nisht vayt iz geven di kasern. bayn undz hot men gezogt kasern dort vu militer iz geven, ikh veys nisht

215
00:11:24,229 --> 00:11:27,173
vi azoy me hot gezogt bay aykh. oykh kasern? yo.

216
00:11:25,222 --> 00:11:26,205
kasern,

217
00:11:26,205 --> 00:11:26,817
yo.

218
00:11:27,173 --> 00:11:33,320
iz, mm dos iz geven umgefer a zekhtsik oder zibetsik kilometer fun undz, deys hot geheysn Toshnad

219
00:11:33,765 --> 00:11:40,045
in ROMÁNIA, nisht vayt fun undz, m'iz geforn mitn RAKEVET, ho'mir ibergeshtign oyf an ander RAKEVET, un m'iz dort gevezn.

220
00:11:40,045 --> 00:11:43,320
un dort ze'mir geven. di ershte tsaytn

221
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,632
iz nisht geven nokh azoy shlekht.

222
00:11:45,632 --> 00:11:49,247
in der heym, di froy mit di tsvey kinder,

223
00:11:50,037 --> 00:11:53,643
hot nokh gehat fun vos tsu lebn, vayl s'iz geblibn in gesheft

224
00:11:53,643 --> 00:11:55,717
zakhn, zi hot farkoyft skhoyres,

225
00:11:55,717 --> 00:11:58,070
un dos lebn iz nokh gegangen.

226
00:11:58,219 --> 00:12:02,001
un dos lebn iz gegangen azoy a shtik tsayt. undz ho'mir di ershte tsaytn

227
00:12:02,001 --> 00:12:05,579
nisht aroysmarshirt vayt, nor m'hot undz gelernt

228
00:12:05,722 --> 00:12:08,183
dort in der SVIVA, oyf di felder,

229
00:12:08,183 --> 00:12:12,003
hot men undz gelernt makhn shitsn-grabn farn militer,

230
00:12:12,003 --> 00:12:13,993
kopen dey shitsn-grabn.

231
00:12:14,196 --> 00:12:17,067
un m'iz arayngegan, esn iz nokh geven gants gut,

232
00:12:17,116 --> 00:12:20,173
in tsveytn teyl iz gevezn, m'hot gehat gelt fun der heym,

233
00:12:20,173 --> 00:12:23,565
un m'hot nokh gekent zikh lozn araynbrengen in di kasern,

234
00:12:23,565 --> 00:12:26,519
un m'hot gehat vos tsu esn. s'iz geven ales, s'iz geven genug.

235
00:12:26,643 --> 00:12:28,169
ikh gedenk nokh a fal,

236
00:12:28,874 --> 00:12:30,939
vayl deys vet mir blaybn in zikorn

237
00:12:32,008 --> 00:12:37,396
bizn tog fun mayn lebn. in a sheynem tog

238
00:12:38,700 --> 00:12:41,839
azoy, arum tsen oder tsvelef tsayt,

239
00:12:42,021 --> 00:12:46,083
kumt aroyf a khaver, vayl dort, s'iz nor geven yidn, ⟨s'iz azoy,⟩ di MUNKÁSSZÁZAD,

240
00:12:46,083 --> 00:12:48,058
di arbayts-dinst, iz geven nor yidn.

241
00:12:48,058 --> 00:12:52,153
kumt aroyf a khaver dort oyvn in, geven oyfn tsveytn shtok ze'mir undz geven,

242
00:12:52,153 --> 00:12:54,682
zogt er, "Meyer," zogt er,

243
00:12:54,956 --> 00:12:58,584
"hintn iz do," zogt er, "epes a shiksl," zogt er, "zi vil dikh zen." zogt er.

244
00:13:00,276 --> 00:13:01,765
shiksl? ver?

245
00:13:03,016 --> 00:13:04,666
ikh loyf arop gikh,

246
00:13:04,733 --> 00:13:08,369
hintn iz geven a brun, di SVIVA fun di goyim

247
00:13:08,369 --> 00:13:14,163
hobn genumen dort gut vaser, vayl di SVIVA iz nisht geven iberal gut vaser, zenen zey arayngekumen in di kasern.

248
00:13:14,664 --> 00:13:17,207
mayn froy olevasholem, di ershte,

249
00:13:17,207 --> 00:13:19,854
hot geshikt mit der tokhter der tsen-yeriker,

250
00:13:20,224 --> 00:13:21,550
a pekl far mir,

251
00:13:21,654 --> 00:13:23,945
un zi iz arayn tsun a goye dortn,

252
00:13:23,945 --> 00:13:27,067
un zi hot zikh ongetun zeyere zakhn, als a goye,

253
00:13:27,133 --> 00:13:30,968
un zi hot genumen in di hant a vyadre un iz arayngekumen tsu di brun nokh vaser

254
00:13:30,968 --> 00:13:33,027
kedey zi zol mir ibergebn dos pekl,

255
00:13:34,363 --> 00:13:38,098
deys gedenk ikh biz dem hayntikn tog un ikh vel es keyn mol nisht fargesn.

256
00:13:37,808 --> 00:13:39,437
vi hot geheysn dos kind?

257
00:13:39,036 --> 00:13:40,924
dos kind hot geheysn Edit.

258
00:13:41,845 --> 00:13:44,641
un shoyn, zi hot mir ibergegebn dos pekl,

259
00:13:44,642 --> 00:13:48,593
ikh hob mit ir geredt a shtikl tsayt in droysn, zi iz gegan mit aza goyish tikhl ongetun,

260
00:13:48,824 --> 00:13:53,535
un di vyadre, zi hot genumen dort ⟨se zol heysn⟩ a bisl vaser, un zi iz zikh avekgegan.

261
00:13:53,535 --> 00:13:55,573
un di tsayt iz gegangen azoy.

262
00:13:55,587 --> 00:13:57,776
ze'mir gevezn dort umgefer

263
00:13:58,531 --> 00:14:00,073
a tsvey yor azoy.

264
00:14:01,814 --> 00:14:02,626
ober

265
00:14:04,852 --> 00:14:08,102
efsher veyniker a khoydesh tsvey, umgefer aza gatung.

266
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:13,501
nokh dem hot men bashlosn me vet undz avekfirn in di berg arayn

267
00:14:13,501 --> 00:14:15,948
vu me makht taken di shitsn-grabn.

268
00:14:15,948 --> 00:14:18,146
do hot men undz nor gelernt vi azoy me makht,

269
00:14:18,161 --> 00:14:20,613
ober me vet undz avekfirn ahin.

270
00:14:22,632 --> 00:14:29,097
mm nishto keyn breyre, keyn sakh zakhn hot men nisht gehat, m'hot nor gehat dos kuferl, un di zakhenes. m'hot zikh genumen

271
00:14:29,684 --> 00:14:34,402
un m'hot zikh tsamgepakt, un dem tsveytn tog hot men undz aroysgefirt tsum RAKEVET,

272
00:14:34,742 --> 00:14:37,904
un me hot undz gefirt, in RAKEVET.

273
00:14:38,195 --> 00:14:41,618
ober der RAKEVET iz geven azoy ful mit mentshn,

274
00:14:41,950 --> 00:14:45,683
az afile in droysn, vu di vagonen bindn zikh tsu eyns dos andere,

275
00:14:45,789 --> 00:14:48,614
iz iz men geshtanen vu m'hot nor gekent.

276
00:14:49,185 --> 00:14:53,165
un ikh bin oykh geven tsishn deye dortn, vayl ikh hob shoyn nisht gehat keyn plats ineveynik.

277
00:14:53,215 --> 00:14:56,447
un dos gerangl, dos geshtupekhts, iz geven azoy groys

278
00:14:56,447 --> 00:14:58,128
az forndik di RAKEVET

279
00:14:58,143 --> 00:15:01,587
hot mikh eyner, tsi velndik tsi nisht-velndik, aropgeshtupt funem RAKEVET.

280
00:15:01,828 --> 00:15:03,988
un ikh bin aruntergefaln untern RAKEVET.

281
00:15:04,329 --> 00:15:07,950
kh'hob gehat groyse shikh, dos mazl iz gevezn,

282
00:15:08,007 --> 00:15:09,056
di finger

283
00:15:09,056 --> 00:15:12,674
funem linkn fus zenen mir geven oyf di GLEIS funem RAKEVET.

284
00:15:13,117 --> 00:15:15,929
un der RAKEVET mit di... iz durkhgeforn nokh.

285
00:15:16,117 --> 00:15:18,570
ikh bin geblibn dort hintn farkhalesht.

286
00:15:19,134 --> 00:15:20,787
un der RAKEVET iz avek.

287
00:15:21,553 --> 00:15:24,836
nokh dem, dortn nisht vayt iz geven aza

288
00:15:25,155 --> 00:15:26,270
aza hayzke,

289
00:15:26,319 --> 00:15:30,816
vu der vos er vos er iz funem RAKEVET varft iber di

290
00:15:30,862 --> 00:15:32,249
di GLEIS

291
00:15:32,249 --> 00:15:34,356
far dem RAKEVET ahin, far dem RAKEVET aher,

292
00:15:34,356 --> 00:15:36,925
der iz gekumen, hot mikh getrofn dortn oyf der erd,

293
00:15:36,973 --> 00:15:39,624
hot er varshayndlekh geklungen, ikh veys nisht vayl

294
00:15:39,624 --> 00:15:43,006
ikh bin geven oyser mir, ikh hob nisht gevust fun mir, hot geklungen,

295
00:15:43,006 --> 00:15:45,407
un s'iz gekumen a militerisher

296
00:15:45,407 --> 00:15:47,590
MAGEN-DAVID, dos heyst

297
00:15:47,590 --> 00:15:49,089
der Royter Kreyts,

298
00:15:49,302 --> 00:15:51,739
un hot mikh arayngefirt. fun dort iz nokh geven,

299
00:15:51,739 --> 00:15:55,714
fun dortn nisht vayt iz geven der hoyptshtot CLUJ, oyb ir hot gehert, KOLOZSVÁR.

300
00:15:55,714 --> 00:15:59,018
der ÚJ KELET shtamt fun dortn, der ungarisher.

301
00:15:59,197 --> 00:16:02,252
m'hot mikh arayngefirt dort in dem BEIT KHOLIM.

302
00:16:03,555 --> 00:16:07,628
dort iz geven loyter ungarn, vayl demolt iz keyn yidn nisht gevezn, deys iz geven Ungarn.

303
00:16:07,628 --> 00:16:09,448
m'hot mikh arayngefirt dortn,

304
00:16:09,466 --> 00:16:13,274
un bald arayngefirt tsun a dokter, un der dokter hot mikh bahandlt

305
00:16:13,868 --> 00:16:18,556
un hot mikh alts oysgefregt, ver ikh bin, fun vu ikh bin, vi azoy ikh bin, vu m'iz geforn.

306
00:16:18,642 --> 00:16:20,945
ikh hob im ales dertseylt, er hot ales farshribn,

307
00:16:21,110 --> 00:16:23,815
un tsu di akht tog

308
00:16:23,959 --> 00:16:27,710
hot men gemakht a NITUAKH, m'hot opgehakt fun di finger dort vu zey zenen gevezn

309
00:16:27,710 --> 00:16:31,268
opgeklemt, un biz dem hayntikn tog iz der linker fus

310
00:16:31,366 --> 00:16:34,650
on a finger. deys iz fun dortn gevezn.

311
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:38,678
un ikh bin dort geven in dem BEIT KHOLIM.

312
00:16:38,895 --> 00:16:40,212
biz

313
00:16:40,437 --> 00:16:42,522
in fir un fertsiker yor,

314
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:45,931
in in feber,

315
00:16:46,359 --> 00:16:48,164
oder shoyn efsher in merts.

316
00:16:48,623 --> 00:16:51,328
un ikh hob bakumen KHOFESH aheymtsuforn.

317
00:16:51,681 --> 00:16:53,064
KHOFESH.

318
00:16:53,087 --> 00:16:54,908
azoy ikh bin geven tsishn di kranke.

319
00:16:55,324 --> 00:16:59,651
ikh bin gegan mit tsvey shtoltsn vayl ikh hob nisht gekent nokh tretn oyfn fus,

320
00:16:59,651 --> 00:17:01,685
hot men mir gegebn KHOFESH aheymtsuforn.

321
00:17:01,685 --> 00:17:03,340
bin aheymgeforn,

322
00:17:03,625 --> 00:17:05,286
nu, in der heym,

323
00:17:05,564 --> 00:17:07,442
mit di froy, mit di tsvey kinder,

324
00:17:08,093 --> 00:17:10,907
un di SAVTA hot nokh gelebt demolt,

325
00:17:10,907 --> 00:17:14,566
zi iz geshtorbn mit a yor shpeter, ikh bin shoyn nisht geven in der heym.

326
00:17:16,430 --> 00:17:18,586
un,

327
00:17:19,270 --> 00:17:21,778
deys iz geven azoy vi ikh zog in merts-tsayt.

328
00:17:22,059 --> 00:17:23,243
april

329
00:17:23,940 --> 00:17:25,566
iz geven peysekh-tsayt,

330
00:17:26,991 --> 00:17:29,664
un nokh peysekh

331
00:17:30,152 --> 00:17:33,467
hot men undz arayngefirt, m'hot gemakht in shtot a geto.

332
00:17:33,991 --> 00:17:35,115
a geto.

333
00:17:35,887 --> 00:17:39,750
m'hot ale yidn tsamgenumen fun yedn hoyz, vu s'iz gevezn,

334
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:43,493
m'hot im gezogt, "kenstu nemen yeder mentsh a valizkele,

335
00:17:43,493 --> 00:17:45,134
pak ayn di zakhn,

336
00:17:45,134 --> 00:17:46,485
pak ayn vos du host

337
00:17:46,556 --> 00:17:49,907
lebns-mitl, nisht keyn shvere zakhenes nor

338
00:17:49,907 --> 00:17:52,820
CAKES un kikhelekh, azoyne zakhn pak ayn,"

339
00:17:52,820 --> 00:17:55,264
un m'hot gebrengt a vogn mit ferd,

340
00:17:55,311 --> 00:17:57,918
un er hot undz arayngefirt in geto.

341
00:17:57,978 --> 00:18:01,568
der geto iz geven gemakht in SATU MARE,

342
00:18:01,568 --> 00:18:05,112
in dem fertl vu di hoypt-yidn hobn gevoynt.

343
00:18:05,553 --> 00:18:10,234
dort iz gevezn, in ek fun der gas hot gevoynt, azoy vi ikh zog aykh, der reb Yoyelish,

344
00:18:10,234 --> 00:18:11,945
un s'iz geven a sakh shtiblekh,

345
00:18:11,945 --> 00:18:14,405
mit rabonim. ikh ken zey nisht oysrekhenen di nemen,

346
00:18:14,419 --> 00:18:15,684
vayl mitn emes gezogt

347
00:18:15,684 --> 00:18:21,059
bin ikh keyn mol nisht gegan ahin, ikh hob zey nisht gekent. ober ikh veys s'iz geven zeyer a sakh. un

348
00:18:21,542 --> 00:18:24,424
ze'mir geven in dem geto umgefer...

349
00:18:24,886 --> 00:18:27,055
ven hot men oyfgemakht dos geto?

350
00:18:26,635 --> 00:18:28,592
dos geto hot men oyfgemakht

351
00:18:30,472 --> 00:18:31,680
mer-veyniker?

352
00:18:31,521 --> 00:18:32,826
mer-veyniker

353
00:18:33,285 --> 00:18:36,375
mit akht tog oder tsvey vokhn far shvues.

354
00:18:36,698 --> 00:18:38,074
in velkhn yor?

355
00:18:38,003 --> 00:18:39,854
in fir un fertsiker yor.

356
00:18:40,035 --> 00:18:42,246
yetst volt ir aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage.

357
00:18:41,289 --> 00:18:42,075
yo.

358
00:18:42,246 --> 00:18:43,660
a bisele tsurik.

359
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:44,250
yo.

360
00:18:44,697 --> 00:18:49,212
fun der tsayt vi m'hot aykh mobilizirt, tsu dey in dem MUNKATÁBOR vos ir hot gezogt,

361
00:18:49,642 --> 00:18:51,406
tsvey un fertsikstn.

362
00:18:50,691 --> 00:18:51,526
yo.

363
00:18:51,900 --> 00:19:00,303
ir hot gevust vos s'tut zikh oyf der velt? ir flegt leyenen a tsaytung, gevust vegn dem az s'tut zikh a velt-milkhome, vos s'tut zikh mit yidn in Poyln, ir hot gehat epes a anung vegn dem?

364
00:18:59,247 --> 00:19:01,126
yo, yo, yo.

365
00:19:00,303 --> 00:19:01,244
vos hot ir gevust?

366
00:19:01,126 --> 00:19:05,724
di zakh, dos heyst, nokh heyder ikh bin arayn in der armey, in tsvey un fertsiker yor,

367
00:19:05,724 --> 00:19:07,160
nokh in di heym,

368
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,474
ho'mir gevust

369
00:19:08,474 --> 00:19:09,765
az se flegn kumen

370
00:19:09,765 --> 00:19:12,172
flikhtlingen, anklofene yidishe

371
00:19:12,632 --> 00:19:15,566
fun Poyln, un zey hobn dertseylt

372
00:19:15,566 --> 00:19:17,803
az me firt avek di yidn,

373
00:19:17,803 --> 00:19:21,484
s'iz do a ort vu se heyst Oyshvits, un dort brengt men um.

374
00:19:21,882 --> 00:19:24,499
un er iz geven bay dem reb Yoyelish un hot dertseylt.

375
00:19:25,528 --> 00:19:30,513
ober di klangen zenen aroysgekumen un yeder hot gevust. ober ver hot zikh gelozt gleybn aza zakh?

376
00:19:30,513 --> 00:19:31,731
se ken nisht zayn!

377
00:19:32,017 --> 00:19:34,291
s'iz nishto aza zakh, az

378
00:19:34,291 --> 00:19:36,893
az me zol nemen mentshn, me zol zey stam hargenen.

379
00:19:36,893 --> 00:19:39,596
un nokh dem iz geven a tsayt,

380
00:19:39,596 --> 00:19:42,251
vos heyder nokh m'hot gemakht dem geto,

381
00:19:42,251 --> 00:19:44,551
un heyder di klangen zenen aroysgekumen,

382
00:19:44,551 --> 00:19:48,857
hot men in shtot, iz geven a sakh yidn vos zey hobn geshtamt fun Poyln.

383
00:19:48,857 --> 00:19:51,361
fun Poyln. zey hobn gevoynt in undzer shtot.

